# No line-ending conversion, ever: the working tree must be byte-identical
# to the blobs so the co-located git bridge (`loot ferry`, ADR 0028) can
# recognize pulled content as already-ingested. With autocrlf smudging, the
# same file has different bytes on disk (CRLF) and in git (LF), and every
# ferry capture spuriously diverges from every ingest.
* -text
